quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  2,49,"Ne olwa khwabahonokosia okhurula khubandu ba Firauni, ababasandinjia eshinyasio eshibii muno, abasinzanga abaana benyu abasiani, ne nibalekha abakhana benyu. Ne mu kano kalimwo amatemo amakhongo okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi."
  2,50,"Ne (yitsulile) olwa khwabaarulila inyanza, ne nikhubahonokosia, ne nikhusishia mumatsi abandu ba Firauni, nanyu nimulolanga."
  2,51,"Ne (yitsulile) olwa khwalaka Musa efilo amakhumi kane (akhole amalaamo malondokhania kho khumuwe Itaurati). Mana nimukhola eshimosi (okhuba Nyasaye wenyu) inyuma wuwe, mana nimuba abakhola obubii."
  2,52,"Mana nikhubaleshela olunyuma lwa ako, kho munyoole okhupa orio."
  2,53,"Ne (yitsulile) olwa khwahelesia Musa Eshitabu (Itaurati) nende Ifurqani (yokhwawukhasia akatoto nende akalali katoto), kho munyole okhulunjikha."
  2,54,"Ne (yitsulile) olwa Musa yaboolela abandu bebe mbu, “Enywe Abandu banje! Toto enywe mwikholeele obubii khulwa okhukhola eshimosi (okhuba Nyasaye wenyu). Kho, sabe eshileshelo khumulonji wenyu, ne mwiyire abene (khukhwira ababii mwinywe). Obo nobulayi khwinywe khumulonji wenyu." Mana nabaleshela. Toto niye Omulesheli muno, Owobukoosia muno."
  2,55,"Ne (yitsulile) olwa mwaboolela Musa mbu, “Shikhulakhusuubila mukokhuboolelanga tawe okhula khulole Nyasaye netsimoni tsiefu.” Mana likulu nilibopa nanyu nimulolanga."
  2,56,"Mana nikhubalamusia okhurula mulifwa lienyu elo kho munyoole okhupa orio."
  2,57,"Mana nikhubahelesia eshinikha shia amaleesi, mana nikhubeshilia Manna nende Salwa (ebilibwa byomwikulu). Lie mubilayi biakhwabakabila. Ne shikhwabakholela obubii tawe, halali abeene nibo bekholelanga obubii."